creator: ChandraMouli Vakkantham
descriptionHtml:
Janmakundali.com a Hyderabad based Astrology portal run by Sri Vakkantham Chandramouli a noted astrologer has launched a Mobile app for android platform.

Telugu people across globed can download this app for free and access Panchangam,Dialy Horoscope and Weekly Horoscope " ON THE GO"

This app will also have various articles written by Sri Vakkantahm on Hindu astrology , Hindu festivals, Vastu and Hindu Dharma which would be updated periodically .

NOTE:

*Panchangam is shown as per IST ( Indian Standard Time ) and Zodiac predictions are based on their Moon signs.
* Content of this app is available in Telugu.
descriptionShort: Astrology portal run by Sri Vakkantham Chandramouli
